@plane z=5 label="Finale"
# Episode 8 — Finale Night

## The Final Vote

**Challenge:** Each finalist creates one piece of content *about* the show itself. Meta-content. Audience votes for the winner.

> "We wanted to see who understood what they'd just been through."
> — EP Marcelline Duvray

### Final Audience Vote Results
| Place | Castmember | Vote % | Prize |
|-------|-----------|--------|-------|
| 🏆 1st | **Chidinma Eze** | 34.2% | $500K + Peacock development deal |
| 2nd | Vesper Quinn | 28.1% | Brand partnership package |
| 3rd | Brecken Vale | 18.4% | — |
| 4th | Nadia Frost | 12.7% | — |
| 5th | Soleil Marsh | 6.6% | — |

---

## Chidinma's Winning Submission
A 90-second dance video. No caption. Every eliminated castmember appears for exactly three seconds.

> Even Kade.

---

**Season 4 greenlit.** Location TBD. Tomas Creed declined to return.
*"I peaked on a disposable camera. Nowhere to go but compressed JPEG."*
